{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312340/extras/20190405_170145.png?t=1732265548\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Introduction</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The original manuscript of this work was completed in early 2015. Please refer to the common sense, standards, rules, etc. in the text at that time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This software is a visual novel with no options at all. The text has been polished and carefully arranged, with 2D illustrations and real-life photos complementing each other, giving new life in a music that matches the atmosphere and is just right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With a text of 110000 words, it describes the different thoughts and romantic love of multiple characters, and constructs a wonderful experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Without much thought about life, Luo Yu accidentally enrolled in Qingling University. By chance, she joined a strange club and met many characters with different personalities. The story begins from then on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players (audience) will take on the role of Luo Yu, experiencing a romantic relationship with the female protagonist day and night, witnessing the joys and sorrows of each character, and moving towards a unique ending driven by fate.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3312340?t=1732265548","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3312340?t=1732265548","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312340/a89f0980a5343fea0413362ae7ceac2190e80ddb/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732265548","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312340/a89f0980a5343fea0413362ae7ceac2190e80ddb/capsule_184